                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17851019-31-defend379 t17851019-31-punish156"></join>
               Privately whipped
            </rs>, And to be sent to his father and mother.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. 
